---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { business } from '../data/site.ts';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Free Website Audit | Meon Valley Web"
  description="Request a free website audit and get a short video review of your site covering speed, mobile usability, SEO basics, security and quick wins."
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: 'Home', href: '/' },
    { name: 'Free website audit' },
  ]}
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-primary-50/30 to-primary-100/50 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="max-w-2xl">
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-black mb-6 leading-[1.1] tracking-tight">
            Free website audit <span class="text-primary-500">for Hampshire businesses</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Send us your website URL and we’ll record a short, personal video review showing what’s working, what’s holding you back, and the quickest wins you can implement.
          </p>
          <a href="#audit-form" class="bg-primary-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-600 transition font-medium text-lg inline-flex items-center justify-center">
            Get my free audit
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-gray-200 p-4 sm:p-6">
          <img
            src="/site-health-bar.webp"
            alt="Example site health score report"
            class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl object-cover"
            width="1090"
            height="790"
            fetchpriority="high"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What the audit covers -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white" aria-label="What the audit covers">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-black mb-4">What we’ll cover in your audit</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">Every audit is a 5–10 minute Loom video walkthrough built from real data, not generic advice.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Speed &amp; Core Web Vitals</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We measure real-world load times, layout stability and interactivity, then flag the fixes that move the needle.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Mobile usability</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">With most visitors now on phones, we check tap targets, font sizing, responsive layout and mobile conversion blockers.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">On-page SEO basics</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Title tags, meta descriptions, headings, internal links and crawlability — the fundamentals Google looks for first.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Security &amp; trust signals</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">SSL status, cookie consent, accessible forms and anything that makes visitors hesitate to get in touch.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Conversion opportunities</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We look at your calls-to-action, contact forms and messaging to spot easy changes that turn more visitors into leads.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Prioritised action list</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">You get a short written summary with fixes ranked by impact and effort, so you know exactly what to tackle first.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Audit request form -->
  <section id="audit-form" class="py-20 bg-primary-500" aria-label="Request your audit">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
        <div class="text-center mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Request your free audit</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">Tell us where to look and where to send the video.</p>
        </div>

        <form name="site-audit" method="POST" data-netlify="true" action="/thank-you-checklist" class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-6">
          <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="site-audit" />
          <div class="hidden" aria-hidden="true">
            <label>Do not fill this out if you are human: <input name="bot-field" type="text" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" /></label>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="audit-url" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Website URL</label>
            <input
              id="audit-url"
              type="url"
              name="website"
              required
              placeholder="https://yourbusiness.co.uk"
              class="w-full px-4 py-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white text-gray-900 placeholder:text-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-200"
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="audit-email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Email address</label>
            <input
              id="audit-email"
              type="email"
              name="email"
              required
              placeholder="your@email.com"
              class="w-full px-4 py-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white text-gray-900 placeholder:text-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-200"
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="audit-name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Your name (optional)</label>
            <input
              id="audit-name"
              type="text"
              name="name"
              placeholder="Jane Smith"
              class="w-full px-4 py-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white text-gray-900 placeholder:text-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-200"
            />
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-gray-900 text-white px-6 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-800 transition font-semibold text-lg">
            Send my free audit
          </button>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 text-center">Free and confidential. No spam. You’ll usually receive your audit within 2 business days.</p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Prefer to talk -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Prefer to chat first?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
        Book a free 30-minute call and we’ll talk through your goals, budget and timeline.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://calendly.com/meonvalleyweb/30min"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-primary-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-600 transition font-medium text-lg"
      >
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
        Book a call
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
